I would expect no such output from Jest

### What is actually happening?
This output is generated:
```
(node:47299) UnhandledPromiseRejectionWarning
(node:47299) UnhandledPromiseRejectionWarning: Unhandled promise rejection. This error originated either by throwing inside of an async function without a catch block, or by rejecting a promise which was not handled with .catch(). (rejection id: 1)
